1.2
log
@define __OpenBSD__ only if defined in build environment, too
same for new __MirBSD__, __MirLinux__
@
text
@/*	$MirBSD$	*/
/*	$OpenBSD: xlint.c,v 1.16 2004/05/11 02:08:07 millert Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: xlint.c,v 1.3 1995/10/23 14:29:30 jpo Exp $	*/

